{"tid":102764,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"機場-夢想啟航的起點","createTime":"2017-01-31T22:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T17:06:09.000Z","uid":27983,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9486d8e308760cf4294a534fea93675668952e5c","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:40:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣覺得每次去到機場就會好似帶俾自己無限可能 一個夢想既開始<br />\n<br />\n好舒服咁享受由出門拉gip 開始既時光<br />\n一到達機場就會掛住睇塊電子板 睇下有咩地方 學埋個英文點讀<br />\n每次都會睇到著哂迷<br />\n<br />\n我諗最放鬆就係個陣 每次等拎行李個陣望到人地係邊到返黎就會諗 如果我有機會去個到就好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇同好？可以分享下你對機場既感覺 經歷<br />\n或者旅遊體驗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/410T250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F410T250.jpg&h=6c08579a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/01/064034_3f1e87fb15228e08477d90175a74cd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F01%2F064034_3f1e87fb15228e08477d90175a74cd0c.jpg&h=84724146&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/01/064035_3f1e87fb15228e08477d90175a74cd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F01%2F064035_3f1e87fb15228e08477d90175a74cd0c.jpg&h=6c65d1e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"656183ba8c7e5ad570d4da8948ff94d4c17c4365","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752d816db59ef1063a9ba58953c29f1380d2b9e1","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d448d6cb9a12f3d1f9566a75b94692c75df0d9","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938ec5a61808508ceadf4e408bcf48c998cc7fad","tid":102764,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:45:47.000Z","msg":"屌, 你係咪痴線, 6:40分開個post, 6:44分推3次, 原本想覆, 而家? 不了"},{"pid":"549eddfd71a93c0039cae566ab130594a1c34575","tid":102764,"uid":54295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:50:30.000Z","msg":"本身係旅行愛好者<br />\n一年都3，4次<br />\n<br />\n但我係返機場工<br />\n所以睇到麻目哂<br />\n<br />\n不過我好鐘意深夜等上機<br />\n第一深夜既機場比較寧靜，好舒服<br />\n第二覺得夜晚既機場比較靚"},{"pid":"21d69756ba772765bc09ebb655aca1448f8409b2","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌, 你係咪痴線, 6:40分開個post, 6:44分推3次, 原本想覆, 而家? 不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n分享下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962ac088cb1c9ca5944c324e07e12846c0090b36","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T22:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身係旅行愛好者<br />\n一年都3，4次<br />\n<br />\n但我係返機場工<br />\n所以睇到麻目哂<br />\n<br />\n不過我好鐘意深夜等上機<br />\n第一深夜既機場比較寧靜，好舒服<br />\n第二覺得夜晚既機場比較靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打最鐘意/想 去邊到"},{"pid":"c9946fb606b7aaf33386b1a9487276cbdf5cba5d","tid":102764,"uid":75452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:30:21.000Z","msg":"成程trip 最期待就係去機場個段路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c48ae0f72b125bf8740a8ea7f9a307d4ddfc6d","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:13:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成程trip 最期待就係去機場個段路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fd3a547b52c4582344a7b4f1e65fd33d6f7373","tid":102764,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:14:45.000Z","msg":"冇，因為香港根本唔係一個講夢想嘅地方。"},{"pid":"3ca7f286abb4ab84e0ecf5fd073346eca6e5c003","tid":102764,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:16:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cdcbdbb06bc08520805a3f26feeab10cecd0353","tid":102764,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:24:37.000Z","msg":"竟然有人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n其他人去機場好似好平常咁<br />\n但我每次去都好開心 好興奮 充滿希望"},{"pid":"efb68d4320c9e9f03dec20ec6db0d6dd0e231aa7","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然有人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n其他人去機場好似好平常咁<br />\n但我每次去都好開心 好興奮 充滿希望</blockquote><br />\n絲打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講出黎 都冇人明"},{"pid":"a89f5979cc175df3a6888d848b793b2b75d670f2","tid":102764,"uid":60736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:32:35.000Z","msg":"次次搭返黎個程就想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cb8e617eccdcf123357918a54fa50aef9fe643","tid":102764,"uid":16070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:34:52.000Z","msg":"我都好鐘意機場  好想瘋狂搭車入機場<br />\n特別係去旅行果陣<br />\n每一個moment都想做幾次<br />\n又見住其他飛機ge牌又好想去埋一份<br />\n總之就好開心好舒服<br />\n不過去完旅行番黎果下真係幾sad<br />\n好似乜都完左咁 好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec586569ec4bd28b336009e43350088e8e45055","tid":102764,"uid":75452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成程trip 最期待就係去機場個段路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身被木村套goodluck洗咗腦 而且赤鱲角比人一種宏大既感覺 人來又人往 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過回程就相反 因為唔想番黎面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a195f12ff89d8313eeb8cfff6931580b7ef64b","tid":102764,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>竟然有人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n其他人去機場好似好平常咁<br />\n但我每次去都好開心 好興奮 充滿希望</blockquote><br />\n絲打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講出黎 都冇人明</blockquote><br />\n第一次旅行係倫敦 9歲 畢生難忘 自此見到飛機都會好激動 好想一齊飛 機場對我來講有特別意義 好多人喊 亦好多人好開心"},{"pid":"460166aa657612eab5ef9aa70a119e641d540975","tid":102764,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次搭返黎個程就想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我由去機場果段路已經想死<br />\n去到check in聽到港豬咯咯咯咯叫直頭無名火起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3c016e2a0d9c6a5880ddd306824eaf57eeb042","tid":102764,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:46:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45ef1ff81be649753c1a5893b080b4ab8825b45d","tid":102764,"uid":48402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人同我一樣覺得每次去到機場就會好似帶俾自己無限可能 一個夢想既開始<br />\n<br />\n好舒服咁享受由出門拉gip 開始既時光<br />\n一到達機場就會掛住睇塊電子板 睇下有咩地方 學埋個英文點讀<br />\n每次都會睇到著哂迷<br />\n<br />\n我諗最放鬆就係個陣 每次等拎行李個陣望到人地係邊到返黎就會諗 如果我有機會去個到就好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇同好？可以分享下你對機場既感覺 經歷<br />\n或者旅遊體驗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/410T250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F410T250.jpg&h=6c08579a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/01/064034_3f1e87fb15228e08477d90175a74cd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F01%2F064034_3f1e87fb15228e08477d90175a74cd0c.jpg&h=84724146&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/01/064035_3f1e87fb15228e08477d90175a74cd0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F01%2F064035_3f1e87fb15228e08477d90175a74cd0c.jpg&h=6c65d1e7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n當你日日返機場你就會知咩叫柴灣同天水圍之戀係幾咁痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46d65bead97cc8aa1e6d68b82f6bd69e9d49ddc","tid":102764,"uid":80110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:24:09.000Z","msg":"係機場返工表示冇咩太大感覺<br />\n只係希望你地去旅行搭A/E車個時傾計可唔可以安靜少少 每次返工放工搭車只係想係車上面訓個教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca95f203716e928cbe461dcff0e2a44dae35325","tid":102764,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:33:35.000Z","msg":"去就開心<br />\n坐A車入去已經覺得在旅途上嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n返黎一去到入境 個人已經乸埋口面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06848fc572d65825367153161017277fb4aac23d","tid":102764,"uid":67779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:34:54.000Z","msg":"其實有無人同我一樣見到機場或者入緊機場個陣有一種好神聖嘅<br />\n特別係香港果個，好似去左世外桃園咁<br />\n每次答A車巴士入機場都會好興奮同埋一D好與別不同的感覺<br />\n就算係去接機每次都會好開心<br />\n睇到人地搭車入去，就算知人地係返工都會好羨慕<br />\n<br />\n係人地機場又唔會咁架WOR，剩係香港果個先會咁<br />\n客運大堂登機果條路，次次搭個扶手電梯，都好似帶你去天堂咁嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S:屌你老母A29，人地架架A車都係廿幾30蚊，偏偏佢就40幾蚊"},{"pid":"e7fbffb7195c6f03ca2bd8e0d37bc273922bb0e1","tid":102764,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"試過搭頭班E車入機場<br />\n<br />\n感覺真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1043fea10968c70b11cb8f7aa4bfeae069b651c","tid":102764,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:57:46.000Z","msg":"去旅行就係，去接機你就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be4420994bb262f49147cacab883f62a246a457","tid":102764,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"Agger ，坐緊A車時已經好似係旅行既一部分咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c232aa8f6650a53e1b4c322d6a9cbb3d1dca5f0f","tid":102764,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"好鍾意去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係坐巴士行嗰段路已經好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過冇野做專登入機場行左個圈 仲上埋觀景台睇飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea062c081976598fc6691a0e38827f034ee8169","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去旅行就係，去接機你就唔同講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我如非必要都唔會去接機<br />\n去機場冇得入離境大堂係好唔開心 會好失落"},{"pid":"a7ac235852d24e6c5e1b9ff95c951bf3112834a4","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>竟然有人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n其他人去機場好似好平常咁<br />\n但我每次去都好開心 好興奮 充滿希望</blockquote><br />\n絲打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講出黎 都冇人明</blockquote><br />\n第一次旅行係倫敦 9歲 畢生難忘 自此見到飛機都會好激動 好想一齊飛 機場對我來講有特別意義 好多人喊 亦好多人好開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望大家有多d一齊飛既時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nenjoy it <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fb4a5c68b5a0a0254e8366163683079c9b6ee3","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好鐘意機場  好想瘋狂搭車入機場<br />\n特別係去旅行果陣<br />\n每一個moment都想做幾次<br />\n又見住其他飛機ge牌又好想去埋一份<br />\n總之就好開心好舒服<br />\n不過去完旅行番黎果下真係幾sad<br />\n好似乜都完左咁 好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返黎個陣揀牌上一個地方 下次去個到"},{"pid":"3d582b9827cc7c5a250bedae5133dc5b2cba536e","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次搭返黎個程就想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會喺人地機場多拍照留念 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0752523b545e542597d0e48520e3a45c4d34eb","tid":102764,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:34:07.000Z","msg":"香港機場真係正<br />\n多謝英國佬<br />\n去過上海關西成田樟宜高雄台北桃園<br />\n無一個夠香港黎<br />\n個個話樟宜正，我又覺得唔夠香港貫通候機室個設計咁宏偉，可能因為CX係喺舊客運大樓啦"},{"pid":"d723d69c6c8ec1ac1624d7337ca998316b6893ae","tid":102764,"uid":42665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"飛好多表示有時候係會好攰<br />\n不過始終都係有啲興奮<br />\n<br />\n最痛苦嘅係莫過睇住隔離登機閘口係班飛香港嘅有人大大聲帶少少粗魯係度講廣東話<br />\n同時你同自己另一半講電話<br />\n聽緊佢有少少唔開心咁問你幾時返<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次都有衝動想上嗰班返香港嘅機<br />\n就算Y我都唔介意<br />\n我淨係上返<br />\n<br />\n但衝動又點喎?<br />\n一次兩次可以咁做啫<br />\n但當你個個禮拜都要飛<br />\n你唔通每次都可以衝動咁返嚟咩?<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n見有巴打話接機好唔快樂<br />\n其實我想講接機畀起自己飛更快樂<br />\n可能係你地未試過成年冇返屋企然後屋企人嚟搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者落左機女朋友好似一個細路咁跑跑跳跳衝入你懷抱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw香港機場係我去過咁多個第二好嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好係章魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8910309e4ba0524a202ef8d172e2ce0b2b04da2","tid":102764,"uid":50554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"細個個陣旅行係好奢侈既事, 而家大個多左廉航而身邊既人都鍾意旅行就會覺得搭飛機好平常<br />\n但每次都好享受係機場既每一刻<br />\n記得有套台劇話一個機場成就左無數人既夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5b69b7e011c121b87db6b082e870ec0afc54f7","tid":102764,"uid":27983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"各位巴打介唔介意分享下想去邊/決定左下個目的地<br />\n<br />\n利伸：中歐"},{"pid":"cba5341e7a612f5ee5cd5ae942f897aa3b7f352c","tid":102764,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴打介唔介意分享下想去邊/決定左下個目的地<br />\n<br />\n利伸：中歐</blockquote><br />\n下一個係名古屋<br />\n再下一個係倫敦<br />\n兩個都plan 好咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715ee22b0789ae89f9ffe776ad4db2b167eea13d","tid":102764,"uid":50554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴打介唔介意分享下想去邊/決定左下個目的地<br />\n<br />\n利伸：中歐</blockquote><br />\n復活節東京<br />\n6月想去越南, 7,8月想去東歐, 不過兩到都未買機票"},{"pid":"ce5bf5730687e5f58f5248603eb29e2539592da4","tid":102764,"uid":9777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:12:07.000Z","msg":"終於有人同我感覺一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好鍾意機場裡面嘅嘢，即使只係一張告示，一個航空用嘅貨櫃，睇到都覺得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31e60e0e6b7fec13e841e4d27dd542feae94296","tid":102764,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於有人同我感覺一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好鍾意機場裡面嘅嘢，即使只係一張告示，一個航空用嘅貨櫃，睇到都覺得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係....好似係唔同既世界咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeba923cc5e03451faa55f7eae756e5c1dbed40a","tid":102764,"uid":69014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:37:29.000Z","msg":"有同感<br />\n直情係有同感到大個都想喺機場搵工做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d37ff32185fe2a30a080d1fa64a394f6e08403","tid":102764,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都好鐘意機場  好想瘋狂搭車入機場<br />\n特別係去旅行果陣<br />\n每一個moment都想做幾次<br />\n又見住其他飛機ge牌又好想去埋一份<br />\n總之就好開心好舒服<br />\n不過去完旅行番黎果下真係幾sad<br />\n好似乜都完左咁 好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返黎個陣揀牌上一個地方 下次去個到</blockquote><br />\n等行李等到躁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd0af187f283eccf48fc1acfb4bed323bfb37f4","tid":102764,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鍾意去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係坐巴士行嗰段路已經好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過冇野做專登入機場行左個圈 仲上埋觀景台睇飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去埋戲院睇戲<br />\n<br />\n食野就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b524e9191d833979f9abbc6f37e07b648f4aa0","tid":102764,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"自己做airline <br />\n出飛既話已經飛到無晒感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旅行既話 一年都飛左十幾次 無左當初旅行好興奮既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉<br />\n<br />\n番工另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91380210e883366957ad049d5b6981794b53804","tid":102764,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴打介唔介意分享下想去邊/決定左下個目的地<br />\n<br />\n利伸：中歐</blockquote><br />\nLA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defd8ac89b3ca0d0b8b599852542239a5e9f5ebe","tid":102764,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"好興奮呀見到呢個post 忍唔住係咁覆呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"fa24402b9de92aefae86496e1bb197c6c118ca2b","tid":102764,"uid":693,"